response.overview: STARDOM is live from Kofu, Yamanashi, Japan on May 25th, 2024. Matches featured • Lady C vs. Sayaka Kurara • STARS (Hanan, Koguma & Saya Iida) vs. Empress Nexus Venus (HANAKO, Waka Tsukiyama & Xena) • Crazy Star (Mei Seira & Suzu Suzuki) vs. Cosmic Angels (Natsupoi & Yuna Mizumori) vs. God's Eye (Saki Kashima & Syuri) • Cosmic Angels (Aya Sakura, Saori Anou & Tam Nakano) vs. God's Eye (Ami Sourei, Konami & Ranna Yagami) • Queen's Quest (AZM, Miyu Amasaki & Saya Kamitani) vs. Oedo Tai (Momo Watanabe, Natsuko Tora & Thekla) • STARS (Hazuki, Mayu Iwatani & Momo Kohgo) vs. Empress Nexus Venus (Maika & Mina Shirakawa) & Starlight Kid. The event was promoted by World Wonder Ring Stardom in the Kose Sports Park Main Arena with attendance reported as 258.
response.title: STARDOM in Kofu • 5.25.2024
